{"tid":2208770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奶茶聯盟》泰國軍警設Road Block　刁難進入曼谷的集會市民　以「顛覆國體」名義查扣書籍","createTime":"2020-09-19T07:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T07:28:44.000Z","uid":35519,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f70bd65d1073348fdf5e9e9b923b1c11013983d6","tid":2208770,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YLMBYtd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYLMBYtd.jpg&h=67d32f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【威權第一步：箝制思想】<br />\n漫長的一天開始了。昨晚已有不少泰國人在網路上回報說，自己從外府要到曼谷參加集會，結果在進曼谷的路段被警察攔下來刁難了很久，目前曼谷各出入口可能都已有泰國警方駐紮盤查。而據媒體報導，目前泰國警方已在集會地點週遭調動了一萬名警力待命。<br />\n<br />\n而今天中午，一組要從法政大學Rangsit校區出發前往集會場地的工作人員，連同載運物品的車輛一起被警方攔下來，警方並查扣了書籍五萬冊，查扣理由是，該書有「顛覆國體」之嫌。<br />\n到底是什麼書？<br />\n<br />\n那是由人權律師Anont及八月十日法政大學集會的骨幹們編寫的小冊，內容是八月十日當天集會中演講內容的合輯，當然最主要的內容就是王室改革的部分，名稱我試譯為《八月撼天：王室改革訴求十點》，華語文化圈應該都能馬上意識到「天」的隱喻是指什麼。<br />\n<br />\n這五萬冊原本是要在集會場地以每本十銖發售，所得資金再繼續印製並發送全國。但目前已經全部被警方扣留。<br />\n<br />\n雖然文宣被扣住很令人氣憤，但除非泰國政府直接把網路封掉，不然是不可能完全抑制資訊流通的，現在都可以用AirDrop互傳線香來線上拜拜了（？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9As5ROi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9As5ROi.jpg&h=49a2d26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ku4nUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ku4nUZ.jpg&h=37d8a187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AO6ismF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAO6ismF.jpg&h=9cd84e9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thematterco/photos/a.1735876059961122/2694484104100308/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthematterco%2Fphotos%2Fa.1735876059961122%2F2694484104100308%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=279e0864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/thematterco/photos/a.1735876059961122/2694484104100308/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n等一下集會就要開始了，滯泰台女的幹話筆記 สาวไต้หวันคุยไม่หยุด有翻譯了他們的戰歌：<br />\n<a href=\"https://reurl.cc/av13Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Freurl.cc%2Fav13Q4&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=898138e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://reurl.cc/av13Q4</a><br />\n<br />\n各地的泰國僑民也動起來了：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tatdnow/photos/a.115391146951482/122702692886994/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftatdnow%2Fphotos%2Fa.115391146951482%2F122702692886994%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=6f0858f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tatdnow/photos/a.115391146951482/122702692886994/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n願人民勝利　|||<br />\n<br />\n原文：泰譯聞 นักแปล กระแสไทย-ไต้หวัน<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThaiChintranslator\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FThaiChintranslator&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=3da9585e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ThaiChintranslator</a>"},{"pid":"00a3f6693e17d4b7d91756ced7303bf93f2b77b5","tid":2208770,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda3421a98032ed7e1c0634c2bec54f0936eb282","tid":2208770,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df0fb29556ad05ad0ca87e465924235957f14e3","tid":2208770,"uid":35519,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"集會戰歌<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/twgirlsganhwa/posts/3321155384667111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftwgirlsganhwa%2Fposts%2F3321155384667111&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=a9407774\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/twgirlsganhwa/posts/3321155384667111</a><br />\n<br />\n歌名：我們是朋友<br />\n樂團：群眾樂團 / The Commoner（วงสามัญชน）<br />\n<br />\n若你聽見震耳樂聲，<br />\n你得去呼朋引伴，<br />\n那是群眾們在躁動，<br />\n是和我們一樣普通的人們。<br />\n<br />\n若你聽見隆隆鼓聲，<br />\n那是群眾們在跺腳，<br />\n響徹雲霄，只因自由的人們集結，<br />\n在同一片天空下。<br />\n<br />\n繁星依舊閃耀，<br />\n熠熠在遠方漆黑的夜空，<br />\n將我們的心繫在一塊，<br />\n堅定信仰，直到我們戰勝的那天。<br />\n<br />\n以鼓掌發出鼓聲，<br />\n發誓不會讓誰，<br />\n來侵犯、剝奪自由的權利，<br />\n只要我們還有一口氣在。<br />\n<br />\n攜手一同向前，<br />\n我們是朋友。"},{"pid":"88a350116ef0d95c179bc328bf0f91bb48da57f9","tid":2208770,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，好大機會包括<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B